ns0:foreignObject.html:div: Look carefully at the image showing elements of the weather. Use what you see to answer the questions. Think about what you've learned in science class so far.

ns0:svg.ns0:text: 1. What is the main topic shown in this picture?
2. Can you count and list the different elements of the weather visible in the image?
3. What do you think the sun is doing in the picture, and how does it affect the weather?
4. How do the elements shown in the picture relate to your daily weather observations?
5. If you were to draw another element of the weather not shown here, what would it be and why?
